Title: GGI Lectures on the Pure Spinor Formalism of the Superstring
Authors: Oscar A. Bedoya and Nathan Berkovits
Abstract: Notes taken by Oscar A. Bedoya of lectures of Nathan Berkovits in June 2009 at the Galileo Galilei Institute School "New Perspectives in String Theory". Topics include the pure spinor superparticle and superstring, tree and loop amplitudes, Ramond-Ramond backgrounds, and open problems.
